  "description": "<i>Chain Reaction</i> is a <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Columns\">Columns</a> clone for one or two players.\nBlocks falls down from the top of the screen in groups of three. Combine three or more blocks of the same color in lines to get points. The more blocks you can remove a time the more points you get. At the earlier levels you can rotate the blocks to best suit your needs but this is not possible on later levels. The game can be played at three levels of difficulty. The harder the game the more colors you have to deal with. Every difficulty level has it's own high score table.",
